Taking my time and doing it my way… Healing has been the focus of my journey, and I can’t wait to share with you all what I been working on during this process. 

HEALING coming to us all very soon! 🙏🏽❄️
#STAYTUNED

❄️LIFE❄️ - Everything but ordinary for a young creative, growing and HEALING in this point in time. Moments that I will forever cherish as we continue to take shit day by day. LOVE to all who stay true to themselves and the mission, WE GOT THIS❤️❄️
#LIFEOFDCMBR ❄️❄️❄️❄️ How y’all think these collabs would sound? 🤔👀🔥
Manifested, Gave me Blessings, That’s How I Knew! — ❄️❄️❄️❄️ — #STAYTUNED

“I’m too proud to let sh*t come btwn me and you now, realize I got a thing for TWO now.. I GOTTA make it, I BETTER make it, I promise if I’m not DEAD then I’m DEDICATED” ❤️ 

To my first born and to the generations before me in this post, I LOVE YOU! Being a father is so amazing, I just pray that God continues to bless & empower me & each of us to be even better! 

OH & one more thing, all I want for this Fathers Day 2023 is for y’all to CLICK THAT LINK IN MY BIO & PRE-SAVE MY NEW SINGLE “HEALING” Dropping June 29th !!!! 😎❄️ Love to all the FATHERS out there, cheers to many more years of family and fellowship 🥂❄️❤️

Music has taken me so many places and helped me see so many things, but all the accolades and success doesn’t mean a thing if you not touching REAL LIVES! Speechless, ONE SINGLE PERSON like myself could move a family enough to share their bond with their child.. I’m no where near where I want to be but I’m constantly reminded that my light extends further than my own understanding. I appreciate all the support and the love over the years. It ain’t NEVER gon stop! #ThankULord #StickTogether

Life update: Still making music for the fun of it. "Love Ain't Free" OUT NOW 🌊 Made this almost a year ago, and wanted to find a way to bring together my love for that cold Toronto rnb sound w the early 2k west coast flavour I grew up on.@jwolf_jwolf and @dcmbrofficial killed this and I'm always grateful to be surrounded by really talented people daily who let me into their worlds - either thru marketing things or producing it's all the same essentially. Enjoy 🌴

DCMBR02 — Love this time of year & I love being able to say that I’m a product of it! Last slide I’m taking yall back to ‘04; my grandpa was the one who laid the foundation for me, so I’m dedicating this post to his remembrance & presence in my life with an old live performance of his in the Gospel world. All this month I’ll be sharing parts of my life that have helped get me this far. Stay tuned for more of DCMBR, for real! ❄️❄️❄️❄️
